cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.CC 

The paper presents a secure data-oblivious shuffle algorithm, which is relevant to cryptography (cs.CR) and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithm can also be used to improve oblivious storage solutions for network-based outsourcing of data, which falls under databases (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and computer communication (cs.CC).
